#block(inset: (left: 20pt), below: 0.2em)[#text(size: 9pt, style: "italic", fill: rgb("#4a5568"))[Tools that shrink, prioritise or restructure context before it reaches the model.]]
#block(inset: (left: 20pt), below: 0.3em)[#text(size: 8.5pt, fill: rgb("#2d3748"))[Middleware focused on making the context window more efficient — pruning, compressing, reordering or mode-switching content for an LLM call. Sits between context assembly and the model itself.]]
