#block(inset: (left: 20pt), below: 0.3em)[#text(size: 8.5pt, fill: rgb("#2d3748"))[Backends that fetch, merge and format context from multiple sources into a prompt-ready payload. The server-side counterpart to context optimisation and visualisation tools.]]
