#block(inset: (left: 20pt), below: 0.2em)[#text(size: 9pt, style: "italic", fill: rgb("#4a5568"))[Dual GUI-and-CLI agent clients offering both graphical and command-line interaction modes.]]
#block(inset: (left: 20pt), below: 0.3em)[#text(size: 8.5pt, fill: rgb("#2d3748"))[Agent frontends that ship as both a graphical desktop app and a command-line tool, sharing a backend. Lets users pick interaction style per task without switching agents.]]
