#block(above: 0.8em, below: 0.3em, inset: (left: 12pt))[#text(size: 12pt, weight: "bold", fill: rgb("#2b6cb0"))[]]
#block(inset: (left: 20pt), below: 0.2em)[#text(size: 9pt, style: "italic", fill: rgb("#4a5568"))[Gateways that compress or distill context before it reaches the model.]]
#block(inset: (left: 20pt), below: 0.3em)[#text(size: 8.5pt, fill: rgb("#2d3748"))[Proxy-layer services that sit between agents and LLMs to shrink prompts, summarize history, or prune tool output, reducing token spend and latency. Distinct from memory systems in that they operate inline on the request path rather than storing state.]]
